(8,	'<p><font style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,102,0); FONT-WEIGHT: bold\" size=\"4\">The Right Place at the Right Price</font>&nbsp; </p>\r\n<div style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 7px; PADDING-LEFT: 7px; PADDING-RIGHT: 7px; FLOAT: right; PADDING-TOP: 0px\"><a href=\"http://www.discovercharlestonwv.com/events/index.php?com=signup\"><img border=\"0\" width=\"250\" height=\"71\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://discovercharlestonwv.com/files/20120425132857.jpg\" /></a><br /></div>\r\n<!-- begin Slider for featured events --><!-- <div style=\"WIDTH: 175px; FLOAT: left\" id=\"wrapper\">\r\n    <div class=\"slider-wrapper theme-default\">\r\n        <div class=\"ribbon\"></div>\r\n        <div id=\"slider\" class=\"nivoSlider\">\r\n            \r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; COLOR: #ff6600\">\r\n        <strong>Featured Events</strong>\r\n    </p>\r\n</div>\r\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"nivo/jquery.nivo.slider.pack.js\"></script>\r\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\r\n	$(window).load(function() {\r\n		$(\'#slider\').nivoSlider({\r\n			directionNav : false,\r\n			controlNav : false\r\n		});\r\n	});\r\n\r\n</script> --><!-- End Slider for featured evets -->\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><font size=\"3\">Are you planning to visit Charleston West Virginia? Whether you are a frequent visitor or a first time guest, Charleston is a city rich in history, commerce, dining, and entertainment. Charleston, the capital city, is family friendly with many fun-filled places to see and activities to do! The surrounding nature of the Appalachian Mountains provides numerous recreational activities and adventures. Charleston is a city that truly offers something for everyone. &nbsp;&nbsp; <br /><br />For business travelers, our Charleston hotels are conveniently located just outside the city, a preferred alternative to downtown, yet well-situated to Charleston&rsquo;s many popular area businesses with easy access by car. Our hotels also offer a complimentary shuttle service to and from Yeager Airport (CRW).&nbsp; <br /><br />Each hotel shares our commitment to excellence that guarantees our guests an enjoyable stay, welcoming service and superb hospitality. Visit one of our outstanding hotels with all of the conveniences and comforts you could need for your visit to Charleston WV. <br /><br />Traveling through? You&rsquo;ll find Charleston WV a perfect central location to stop for a relaxing break. We are central and midpoint to travels between the following cities and states: </font></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><font size=\"3\">Under 250 miles: <br />Charlotte, Richmond, Pittsburgh, Cleveland, Louisville, Washington DC <br /></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><font size=\"3\">Under 500 miles: <br />Detroit, Toronto, NYC, Nashville, Indianapolis, Chicago </font></p>\r\n<br /><hr align=\"center\" color=\"#000000\" />\r\n<h2 style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,102,0)\" align=\"center\">Superior Charleston West Virginia Hotels:</h2>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><font size=\"3\">For family vacations, weekend getaways, leisure or business travel, our portfolio of Charleston West Virginia hotels provides convenient and comfortable hotel accommodations in nationally recognized hospitality brands such as Hampton, the Holiday Inn & Suites Charleston West&nbsp;and Wingate:</font> </p>\r\n<p><font size=\"3\"><br /><strong><script type=\"text/javascript\">\r\n			document.write(\'<a href=\"http://hamptoncharleston.com\" onclick=\"recordOutboundLink(this, \\\'main page link\\\', \\\'hamptoncharleston.com\\\');return false;\">\');\r\n\r\n        </script>Choose Hampton Inn <script>\r\n			document.write(\'</a>\');\r\n        </script></strong></font><font size=\"3\"><br />When traveling in the Charleston West Virginia area, check into Hampton Inn Southridge and see what real comfort is all about.</font><font size=\"3\"><strong> Expanded and fully renovated,</strong> this is a premier hotel in the Charleston and Southridge area. The hotel is conveniently situated directly on Route 119, off Interstate 64 and is located in the heart of the large and busy Southridge shopping district in the Charleston area, you will enjoy a wide range of restaurants and retail stores to choose from during your stay. </font></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><font size=\"3\">With two bedded rooms, king rooms, kitchen studios and suites with in-room hot tubs, the Hampton Inn Southridge will have just the right room for you.</font><font size=\"3\"> All this and you&rsquo;re only 10 minutes from downtown Charleston!</font> <br /><font size=\"3\"><br /><strong><script type=\"text/javascript\">\r\n			document.write(\'<a href=\"http://hicharleston.com\" onclick=\"recordOutboundLink(this, \\\'main page link\\\', \\\'hicharleston.com\\\');return false;\">\');\r\n\r\n        </script>Stay Refreshed at The Holiday Inn & Suites Charleston West <br /></strong></font><script>\r\n		document.write(\'</a>\');\r\n    </script></p>\r\n<div style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><font size=\"3\">For meetings ranging from 10 to over 1,000 or for a family fun-filled vacation, The&nbsp;Holiday Inn & Suites Charleston West, <em>formerly the Ramada Charleston</em>,&nbsp;is the hotel in the city to make your stay truly memorable and deliver the very best value. Currently undergoing renovations of the lobby, pool&nbsp;and other public areas, the hotel&nbsp;is in the middle of a major transformation to become one of the area&rsquo;s most desirable meeting and vacation locations. </font></div>\r\n<div style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><font size=\"3\">The Holiday Inn & Suites Charleston West&nbsp;is located only 5 minutes from downtown Charleston and close to all major area attractions. The hotel is situated directly off Interstate 64. <br /></font><font size=\"3\"><br /><strong><script type=\"text/javascript\">\r\n			document.write(\'<a href=\"http://wingatecharleston.com\" onclick=\"recordOutboundLink(this, \\\'main page link\\\', \\\'wingatecharleston.com\\\');return false;\">\');\r\n\r\n        </script>Wingate by Wyndham: The perfect choice for Charleston business <script>\r\n        document.write(\'</a>\');\r\n        </script><br /></strong></font></div>\r\n<div style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\">\r\n<div style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\">\r\n<p><font size=\"3\">Conveniently located just five minutes from downtown Charleston with optimal amenities designed for business travelers. The Wingate&rsquo;s meeting facilities are an ideal setting for board meetings, luncheons, team meetings, and seminars. <br />If you travel for sales and need to be centrally located, we are the ideal location for you.</font> </p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><font size=\"3\">The Wingate is located only 5 minutes from downtown Charleston and close to all the major area attractions. The hotel is situated directly off Interstate 64. </font></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; </p>\r\n</div>',	'home',	20080619100000,	'Discover Charleston West Virginia',	NULL,	NULL,	0,	20120525093059,	'top'),
(40,	'<h1 style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,102,0)\"><font size=\"4\">Charleston Hotel Reservations for West Virginia Vacations, Business Travel and Meetings</font></h1>\r\n<p align=\"justify\">We look forward to welcoming you to our hotels on your vacation, business stay or meeting in Charleston West Virginia. With the newly renovated and expanded Hampton Inn, Southridge, the contemporary Wingate by Wyndham or the Holiday Inn &amp; Suites Charleston West, Charleston&rsquo;s most recently fully-renovated hotel and conference center, you&rsquo;ll be welcomed with premium amenities and exceptional hospitality. It will be our pleasure to take care of all your travel needs. You will experience Charleston at its best with our family of team members and hotels.</p>\r\n<p align=\"justify\">All our hotels are located off 3 major Interstate highways which are central between major cities: Interstate 64, Interstate 77 and Interstate 79.<br />Heading in any direction on these highways between Pittsburgh and Lousiville, Cleveland and Charlotte or Cincinnati and Raleigh, you&rsquo;ll find Charleston the perfect mid point in your journey.</p>\r\n<hr width=\"100%\" size=\"1\" color=\"#e8ede4\" />\r\n<p><strong>All our hotels feature </strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>complimentary expanded hot breakfast </li>\r\n    <li>complimentary wireless high speed internet access </li>\r\n    <li>free parking </li>\r\n    <li>shuttle service within a 5 mile radius </li>\r\n    <li>large suites and rooms with hot tubs </li>\r\n    <li>access to large swimming pool and hot tub </li>\r\n    <li>free use of fully equipped Business Centers </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p align=\"justify\">Whether your visit to Charleston is for leisure, business or a conference, our staff is experienced, excited and trained to make sure your stay and your meetings are perfect!</p>\r\n<hr width=\"100%\" size=\"1\" color=\"#e8ede4\" />\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><strong>Online Reservations:</strong><br />Plan your stay at any of our Charleston West Virginia hotels through our easy-to-use and secure online reservations systems. Packages are also available for online booking (some packages are only available by contacting the hotel directly). </p>\r\n<hr width=\"100%\" size=\"1\" color=\"#e8ede4\" />\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><strong><script type=\"text/javascript\">\r\n	document.write(\'<a href=\"http://hamptoninn.hilton.com/en/hp/hotels/index.jhtml?ctyhocn=CRWSOHX\" onclick=\"recordOutboundLink(this, \\\'reservations page link\\\', \\\'Hampton.com\\\');return false;\">\');\r\n		</script>Hampton Inn Charleston<script>document.write(\'</a>\');</script> <br /></strong>Located in the heart of the Southridge district with major national retailers and outlet stores within a 2 mile radius, you can enjoy restaurants, shopping and still be within 10 minutes from downtown Charleston. All rooms are oversized with microwaves, refrigerators and in-room safes.Perfect for business travelers as well as for your vacation.<br /></p>\r\n<br />For the most substantial upgrade in Charleston, the Hampton Inn, Southridge,&nbsp;has upgraded their Lobby, Breakfast and Dining areas, put in a newly expanded and&nbsp;State of the Art Fitness Center, and renovated the pool and hot tub, adding new, private cabanas.\r\n<p><strong></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Hotel Amenities:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Microwaves and refrigerators as a standard feature </li>\r\n    <li>Flat panel high definition TV monitors for an enhanced viewing experience </li>\r\n    <li>Laptop-sized safes in all rooms </li>\r\n    <li>Our featured indoor pool with private cabanas, hot tub and State of the art Fitness center </li>\r\n    <li>Complimentary use of fully equipped Business Center </li>\r\n    <li>Signature amenity: free fountain soft drinks available 24 hours daily! </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Phone:304-746-4646</strong></p>\r\n<hr width=\"100%\" size=\"1\" color=\"#e8ede4\" />\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><strong><script type=\"text/javascript\">\r\n	document.write(\'<a href=\"http://www.holidayinn.com/redirect?path=hd&brandCode=hi&localeCode=en&regionCode=1&hotelCode=CRWCH&_PMID=99502222\" onclick=\"recordOutboundLink(this, \\\'reservations page link\\\', \\\'holiday Inn\\\');return false;\">\');\r\n		</script>Holiday Inn &amp; Suites Charleston West</strong><script>document.write(\'</a>\');</script> <br />The former Ramada&nbsp;Charleston,&nbsp;now the&nbsp;Holiday Inn &amp; Suites Charleston West is&nbsp;&nbsp;Charleston&rsquo;s largest hotel surrounding downtown Charleston (only 10 minutes to downtown) featuring</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>newly renovated, full conference center facilities catering for over 1,000 people </li>\r\n    <li>state of the art audio-visual services in conference rooms </li>\r\n    <li>complimentary use of fully equipped Business Center </li>\r\n    <li>Newly remodeled Pool and Spa</li>\r\n    <li>Free ground level parking </li>\r\n    <li>Newly renovated public areas </li>\r\n    <li>Renovated restaurant and lounge </li>\r\n    <li>Rooms that have undergone substantial renovation featuring new carpets, furniture and fixtures </li>\r\n    <li>Guestroom bathrooms renovated for a contemporary and upscale presentation </li>\r\n    <li>Comedy Zone entertainment featuring the best comedy in West Virginia!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>\r\n<p><strong>Phone:304-744-4641</strong></p>\r\n<hr width=\"100%\" size=\"1\" color=\"#e8ede4\" />\r\n<p><strong><script type=\"text/javascript\">\r\n	document.write(\'<a href=\"http://www.wingatehotels.com/Wingate/control/Booking/check_avail?checkInDate=06/29&checkOutDate=06/30&numberRooms=1&numberAdults=1&numberChildren=0&rate=000&force_nostay=false&id=10115&propBrandId=WG&intcmp=16878&corporateCode=1000002810&referUrl=http://www.wyndham.com\" onclick=\"recordOutboundLink(this, \\\'reservations page link\\\', \\\'Wyndham.com\\\');return false;\">\');\r\n		</script>Wingate by Wyndham Charleston<script>document.write(\'</a>\');</script> </strong></p>\r\n</strong>\r\n<p align=\"justify\">The Wingate by Wyndham is Charleston&rsquo;s hotel designed perfectly for the business traveler.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Each room is Business Class with an executive desk and ergonomic recliner </li>\r\n    <li>Microwave and refrigerator in every room </li>\r\n    <li>Three conference rooms with full catering facilities </li>\r\n    <li>Large fitness center with oversize hot tub. </li>\r\n    <li>Complimentary use of fully equipped Business Center </li>\r\n    <li>Featuring the Wyndham Hotels signature bed with duvet, upgraded choice of pillows and linens. </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p align=\"justify\">For those who need more spacious accommodations, we offer large suites as well as some with in-room hot tubs.&nbsp; <br />All guests of the Wingate by Wyndham are welcome to use the swimming pool and hot tub at the&nbsp;Holiday Inn &amp; Suites Charleston West located directly adjacent.</p>\r\n<p align=\"justify\">Whatever your reason, you&rsquo;ll find the Wingate by Wyndham, Charleston, a perfect home&hellip;or home office.</p>\r\n<strong><strong>Phone: 304-744-4444</strong></strong>',	'Reservations',	20080619100000,	'Reservations',	NULL,	NULL,	0,	20140226100105,	'top'),
(41,	'<h1 style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,102,0)\"><font size=\"4\">Charleston West Virginia Hotel Specials and Getaway Packages </font></h1>\r\n<p align=\"justify\">For your next travel getaway, whether vacation or business, enjoy a hotel stay in one of our three exceptional Charleston, West Virginia hotels. Our convenient locations near downtown Charleston are situated just miles from Yeager Airport (CRW), local area business, tourist attractions, shopping, restaurants, and more. For Charleston West Virginia travel, look no further than our Charleston West Virginia hotels!<br /><br />Our hotels offer a variety of Specials &amp; Packages to help you experience West Virginia at its best.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><font color=\"#0000ff\"><font size=\"4\">Hampton Inn Southridge Specials</font>&nbsp;</font></strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table cellspacing=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" border=\"0\" style=\"width: 207px; height: 228px;\" summary=\"\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://hamptoncharleston.com/page/?item=5&amp;title=Romance+Getaway\"><img width=\"150\" border=\"0\" height=\"188\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://discovercharlestonwv.com/files/20120202100717.jpg\" /></a>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://hamptoncharleston.com/page/?item=5&amp;title=Romance+Getaway\"><font size=\"4\">Romantic Getaway</font></a></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><font size=\"4\" color=\"#3d9b35\"><strong>Holiday Inn &amp; Suites Charleston West Specials</strong></font></p>\r\n<table cellspacing=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" border=\"0\" align=\"left\" summary=\"\" style=\"width: 700px; height: 228px;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"205\" valign=\"middle\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.hicharleston.com/page/?item=5&amp;title=Comedy+Zone+Package\"><img width=\"150\" align=\"middle\" height=\"188\" src=\"http://discovercharlestonwv.com/file