(43,	'<h1 style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,102,0)\"><font size=\"4\">Contact any of our collection of Charleston Area West Virginia Hotels</font></h1>\r\n<p>We are always available to assist you with inquiries or special requests. Call, fax or email 24 hours a day. </p>\r\n<p><strong>Hampton Inn</strong> <br />1 Preferred Place <br />Charleston, WV 25309 <br />Phone:(304) 746-4646 <br />Fax: (304) 746-4665 <br />Email: <a href=\"mailto:infohampton@DiscoverCharlestonWV.com\">infohampton@DiscoverCharlestonWV.com</a> <br /></p>\r\n<hr width=\"100%\" size=\"1\" color=\"#e8ede4\" />\r\n<p><strong>Holiday Inn &amp; Suites Charleston West Hotel</strong> <br />400 Second Avenue <br />Charleston, WV 25303 <br />Phone: (304) 744-4641 <br />Fax: (304) 744-4525 <br />Email: <a href=\"mailto:webinfo@DiscoverCharlestonWV.com\">webinfo@DiscoverCharlestonWV.com</a> <br /></p>\r\n<hr width=\"100%\" size=\"1\" color=\"#e8ede4\" />\r\n<p><strong>Wingate by Wyndham </strong><br />402 Second Ave <br />Charleston, WV 25303 <br />Phone: 304)-744-4444 <br />Fax: (304)-744-4343 <br />Email: <a href=\"mailto:infowingate@DiscoverCharlestonWV.com\">infowingate@DiscoverCharlestonWV.com</a> <br /></p>\r\n<hr width=\"100%\" size=\"1\" color=\"#e8ede4\" />\r\n<h2 style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,102,0)\"><font size=\"4\">FAQ</font></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li><a href=\"#1\">Holiday Inn &amp; Suites Charleston West</a>&nbsp; </li>\r\n    <li><a href=\"#3\">Hampton Inn - Southridge, Charleston</a> </li>\r\n    <li><a href=\"#2\">Wingate by Wyndham, Charleston</a> </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<hr width=\"100%\" size=\"1\" color=\"#e8ede4\" />\r\n<h3><font size=\"4\" style=\"COLOR: #3d9b35\">HOLIDAY INN &amp; SUITES CHARLESTON WEST HOTEL</font><a name=\"1\" id=\"1\"></a></h3>\r\n<p><strong>Q</strong>. <strong>How far are you from Yeager Airport?</strong> <br /><strong>A.</strong> We are just over 8 miles west of the Yeager Airport (CRW).&nbsp; Depending on traffic, this is usually a 10-15 minute drive. <br /><br /><strong>Q.&nbsp; Do you have shuttle service?</strong> <br /><strong>A.</strong>&nbsp; The Holiday Inn &amp; Suites Charleston West&nbsp;offers complimentary transportation to and from Yeager airport.&nbsp; </p>\r\n<p><strong>Q. Do you accept pets in the rooms? <br />A.</strong> We do offer a number of pet-friendly rooms, which are located on the third floor of the hotel. All pet rooms are smoking rooms. There is a pet fee of $25 + tax per night per pet. </p>\r\n<p><strong>Q. Do you have internet access? <br />A.</strong> Yes, we provide complimentary Wireless High-Speed Internet access in all guestrooms and in the lobby, recreational areas and the Cafe. We also offer a complimentary business center in the lobby with a computer workstation with Internet access and a self-service printer. A copier and fax machine are available at the front desk. <br /><br /><strong>Reservations confirmation and guarantee policy: </strong><br />A credit card is required as a guarantee on reservations, and a valid card must be presented at check in. Any reservation made without a guarantee will be cancelled at 4pm on the day of arrival unless special arrangements have been made. Faxed or mailed confirmation letters are available upon request. <br /><br /><strong>Cancellations and charges: </strong><br />The hotel has a 4pm cancellation policy. Any guaranteed reservation not cancelled by 4pm the day of arrival will be charged a no-show charge of the entire room rate. <br /><br /><strong>Check in and Checkout times:</strong> <br />Check-in time is 3:00pm, and all guaranteed reservations can check in any time after 3:00. Checkout time is 12 noon. Early check-in and late checkouts can be arranged for guests with special needs. Please inquire with the front desk. <br /><br /><strong>Entrances and security to the hotel: </strong><br />All doors and gates to the hotel are either only accessible by a guest cardkey or are locked after 9pm. The lobby entrance to the front desk is open 24 hours and we have 24-hour staff on property at night. <br /><br /><strong>Facilities for Guests with Disabilities</strong>: <br />The Holiday Inn &amp; Suites Charleston West has ADA accessible public restrooms in the lobby of the hotel. ADA accessible guestrooms are available and should be requested at the time of making your reservation. Devices for the hearing impaired are available from the Front Desk. </p>\r\n<p><strong>Q. Do you have a swimming pool? <br />A.</strong> Yes. Use of our pool is complimentary to Holiday Inn &amp; Suites Charleston West&nbsp; and Wingate Inn guests only. Pool depth a maximum of 4 1/2 ft and there is no lifeguard on duty. <br /><br /></p>\r\n<hr width=\"100%\" size=\"1\" color=\"#e8ede4\" />\r\n<h3><font size=\"4\" style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,51,0)\"><span style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,102,0)\">WINGATE BY WYNDHAM</span> </font><a name=\"2\" id=\"2\"></a></h3>\r\n<p><strong>Q.&nbsp; How far are you from Yeager Airport?</strong> <br /><strong>A</strong>. We are just over 8 miles west of the Yeager Airport (CRW).&nbsp; Depending on traffic, this is usually a 10-15 minute drive. </p>\r\n<p><strong>Q.&nbsp; Do you have shuttle service?</strong> <br /><strong>A.&nbsp;</strong> The Wingate offers complimentary transportation to and from Yeager airport.&nbsp; <br /><br /><strong>Reservations confirmation and guarantee policy: </strong><br />A credit card is required as a guarantee on reservations, and a valid card must be presented at check in. Any reservation made without a guarantee will be cancelled at 4pm on the day of arrival unless special arrangements have been made. Faxed or mailed confirmation letters are available upon request. <br /><br /><strong>Cancellations and charges: </strong><br />The hotel has a 4pm cancellation policy. Any guaranteed reservation not cancelled by 4pm the day of arrival will be charged a no-show charge of the entire room rate. <br /><br /><strong>Check in and Checkout times: </strong><br />Check-in time is 3:00pm, and all guaranteed reservations can check in any time after 3:00. Checkout time is 12 noon. Early check-in and late checkouts can be arranged for guests with special needs. Please inquire with the front desk. <br /><br /><strong>Entrances and security to the hotel: </strong><br />All doors and gates to the hotel are either only accessible by a guest cardkey or are locked after 9pm. The lobby entrance to the front desk is open 24 hours and we have 24-hour staff on property at night. <br /><br /><strong>Facilities for Guests with Disabilities: </strong><br />The Wingate has ADA accessible public restrooms in the lobby of the hotel. ADA accessible guestrooms are available and should be requested at the time of making your reservation. Devices for the hearing impaired are available from the Front Desk. <br /><br /><strong>Q.&nbsp; Do you accept pets in the rooms?</strong> <br /><strong>A.</strong>&nbsp; We do not offer pet rooms. If you require a pet room, please visit the Holiday Inn &amp; Suites Charleston West located next door. We are happy to make those arrangements for you, if you wish. <br /><br /><strong>Q.&nbsp; Do you have internet access?</strong> <br /><strong>A.&nbsp;</strong> Yes, we provide complimentary Wireless High-Speed Internet access in all guestrooms and in the lobby. Wired plug-in internet access with Ethernet cables are available in all rooms. We also offer a complimentary business center in the lobby with a computer workstation with Internet access and a self-service printer, copier and fax machine. </p>\r\n<p><strong>Q.</strong>&nbsp; <strong>Do you have a swimming pool?</strong> <br /><strong>A.</strong>&nbsp; No. However, we do have a large hot tub and Fitness Center at the hotel. Our sister hotel, The Holiday Inn &amp; Suites Charleston West, is directly adjacent to the Wingate and has an atrium style pool and large hot tub open to Wingate Inn guests. </p>\r\n<hr width=\"100%\" size=\"1\" color=\"#e8ede4\" />\r\n<h3><font size=\"4\" style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,51,0)\"><span style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,102,0)\">HAMPTON INN, SOUTHRIDGE</span> </font><a name=\"3\" id=\"3\"></a></h3>\r\n<p><strong>Q.&nbsp; How far are you from Yeager Airport?</strong> <br /><strong>A.</strong> We are just over 10 miles west of the Yeager Airport (CRW).&nbsp; Depending on traffic, this is usually a 15-20 minute drive. </p>\r\n<p><strong>Q.&nbsp; Do you have shuttle service?</strong> <br /><strong>A.</strong>&nbsp; The Hampton Inn Southridge offers complimentary transportation to and from Yeager airport.&nbsp; </p>\r\n<p><strong>Q. Do you accept pets in the rooms? <br />A.</strong> We do not offer pet rooms. If you need a pet room, please visit our sister property, the Holiday Inn &amp; Suites Charleston West. </p>\r\n<p><strong>Q. Do you have internet access? <br />A. </strong>Yes, we provide complimentary Wireless High-Speed Internet access in all guestrooms and in the lobby. We also offer a complimentary business center in the lobby with a computer workstation with Internet access and a self-service printer, copier and fax machine. </p>\r\n<p><strong>Q. Do you have a swimming pool? <br />A.</strong> Yes. Use of our pool is complimentary to Hampton Inn guests only. Pool depth is 3 ft and there is no lifeguard on duty. <br /><br /><strong>Reservations confirmation and guarantee policy: </strong><br />A credit card is required as a guarantee on reservations, and a valid card must be presented at check in. Any reservation made without a guarantee will be cancelled at 6pm on the day of arrival unless special arrangements have been made. Faxed, emailed or mailed confirmation letters are available upon request. <br /><br /><strong>Cancellations and charges: </strong><br />The hotel has a 6pm cancellation policy. Any guaranteed reservation not cancelled by 6pm the day of arrival will be charged a no-show charge of the entire room rate. <br /><br /><strong>Check in and Checkout times: </strong><br />Check-in time is 3:00pm, and all guaranteed reservations can check in any time after 3:00. Checkout time is 12 noon. Early check-in and late checkouts can be arranged for guests with special needs, please inquire with the front desk. <br /><br /><strong>Entrances and security to the hotel:</strong> <br />All doors and gates to the hotel are either only accessible by a guest cardkey or are locked after 9pm. The lobby entrance to the front desk is open 24 hours and we have 24-hour staff on property at night. <br /><br /><strong>Facilities for Guests with Disabilities:</strong> <br />The Hampton Inn Southridge has ADA accessible public restrooms in the lobby of the hotel. ADA accessible guestrooms are available and should be requested at the time of making your reservation. Devices for the hearing impaired are available from the Front Desk. </p>',	'Contact',	20080619100000,	'Contact Us',	NULL,	NULL,	0,	20140228094750,	'top'),
(44,	'<h1 style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,102,0)\"><font size=\"4\">Plan your Charleston West Virginia Vacation Getaways</font></h1>\r\n<p align=\"justify\">Enjoy a quick getaway or a relaxing vacation stay in Charleston West Virginia! With countless activities rich in history and culture, or adventurist and wild in nature, Charleston offers something for every taste. Fill your days with festivals, historical reenactments, shopping and more. Or get out and take pleasure in the Appalachian Mountains with great hiking, white water rafting and biking. Make it easy with one of our great hotel packages, complete with activities, gifts and great accommodations. For your leisure travels in West Virginia, our Charleston Hotels are committed to making your hotel stay enjoyable and relaxing. <br /><br />Typical leisure travel amenities and services at our Charleston WV Hotels include:<br /><br /></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Fitness Room </li>\r\n    <li>Indoor Pool/Jacuzzi </li>\r\n    <li>Airport Shuttle </li>\r\n    <li>On-site Restaurant/Lounge (Holiday Inn & Suites Charleston West) </li>\r\n    <li>Restaurants nearby (Hampton Inn and Wingate) </li>\r\n    <li>Comedy Zone (Comedy entertainment weekends at Holiday Inn & Suites Charleston West) </li>\r\n    <li>Free Local Phone Calls </li>\r\n    <li>Free parking </li>\r\n    <li>Business Center </li>\r\n    <li>Free high speed internet access </li>\r\n    <li>Coffee maker </li>\r\n    <li>Iron/ironing board </li>\r\n    <li>Alarm clock/wakeup service </li>\r\n</ul>',	'Leisure',	20080619100000,	'Leisure Travel',	NULL,	NULL,	0,	20120525090924,	'left'),
(45,	'<h1 style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><font size=\"4\">Our business is making your business stay convenient and enjoyable </font></h1>\r\n<p>Our family of Charleston West Virginia hotels offers a variety of business services and amenities to make your stay as convenient, productive and as enjoyable as possible. The hotels are in ideal locations just minutes from downtown Charleston, and fifteen minutes from Yeager Airport (CRW). </p>\r\nBusiness features include complimentary high-speed internet access, voicemail, wake up service, in room work desks, airport shuttles and more. Our hotels also feature a variety of function and meeting spaces that are ideal for banquets, luncheons, meetings, and seminars; all complimented with exceptional service and superior hospitality.',	'Business',	20080619100000,	'Business Travel',	NULL,	NULL,	0,	20120525090934,	'left'),
(46,	'<h1 style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,102,0)\"><font size=\"4\">Successful Meetings and Group Events!</font></h1>\r\n<h2 style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,102,0)\"><font size=\"3\">Let us help you plan and host your next Charleston Meeting, Wedding or Special Event!</font></h2>\r\n<p align=\"justify\">The possibilities are endless for your next business meeting or group travel to Charleston, when you choose any of our Hotels Charleston WV properties to plan and host your event! Our facilities provide a variety of flexible meeting space with premium amenities, full catering services, ideal for small group banquets and events, or corporate meetings and business group gatherings. From planning to event implementation, our experienced staff is dedicated to exceptional service for the success of your event! <br /><br />Each of our hotels in Charleston, West Virginia offer various meeting and event facility options. Please click on the hotel below for further detail on each property and to find the property that best suits all of your meeting and group needs and interests:</p>\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><a href=\"http://www.hamptoncharleston.com/\"><strong>Hampton Inn Charleston</strong></a><br />Our hotel features one meeting room that can be divided into two separate rooms, hosting up to 40 people in a variety of set-up styles. </p>\r\n<hr color=\"#e8ede4\" size=\"1\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><a href=\"http://www.hicharleston.com/\"><strong>Holiday Inn & Suites Charleston West Hotel </strong></a><br />Over 8900 square feet in a variety of rooms and halls providing flexible event space ideal for business and social events up to 400 people. Full catering options available. </p>\r\n<hr color=\"#e8ede4\" size=\"1\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><a href=\"http://wingatecharleston.com/\"><strong>Wingate by Wyndham Charleston</strong></a><br />Meeting and board room facilities with a variety of set up options available, ideal for small business groups up to 40 people. Catering available through the Holiday Inn & Suites Charleston West. </p>',	'Meetings',	20080619100000,	'Meetings & Groups',	NULL,	NULL,	0,	20120525091011,	'left'),
(47,	'<h1 style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,102,0)\"><font size=\"4\">Charleston West Virginia History, Attractions and Travel Guide </font></h1>\r\n<h2 style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,102,0)\"><font size=\"3\">Live the history of Charleston West Virginia</font></h2>\r\n<div style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><font size=\"4\"><font size=\"3\">Charleston West Virginia is an unexpected haven for adventurous and astonishing vacation getaways. Families and friends can enjoy adventures rich in history and culture from Civil War reenactments, to Appalachian music, to festivals, and more. Surrounded by the Appalachian Mountains, Charleston is a city filled with much more than just history. Minutes away from the heart of the city, nature lovers can find exciting activities such as hiking, rafting, skiing, biking, and more.</font>&nbsp;</font></div>\r\n<h2 style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,102,0)\"><font size=\"3\">Local Attractions</font></h2>\r\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" align=\"center\" summary=\"\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"160\" valign=\"top\" align=\"center\" style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 10px; PADDING-LEFT: 10px; PADDING-RIGHT: 10px; PADDING-TOP: 10px\"><a href=\"http://discovercharlestonwv.com/page.php?it=31\"><img width=\"150\" border=\"0\" height=\"188\" alt=\"Capitol Market - Food, Art &amp; Fun. A Charleston WV Attraction\" src=\"http://discovercharlestonwv.com/files/20110819095407.jpg\" /></a> </td>\r\n            <td width=\"160\" valign=\"top\" align=\"center\" style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 10px; PADDING-LEFT: 10px; PADDING-RIGHT: 10px; PADDING-TOP: 10px\"><a href=\"http://discovercharlestonwv.com/page.php?it=35\"><img width=\"150\" border=\"0\" height=\"188\" alt=\"The Clay Center - Explore, Experience, Engage!\" src=\"http://discovercharlestonwv.com/files/20110824125854.jpg\" /></a></td>\r\n            <td width=\"160\" valign=\"top\" align=\"center\" style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 10px; PADDING-LEFT: 10px; PADDING-RIGHT: 10px; PADDING-TOP: 10px\"><a href=\"http://discovercharlestonwv.com/page.php?it=42\"><img width=\"150\" border=\"0\" height=\"188\" alt=\"WV Cultural Center &amp; Museum - History, Culture, Theatre all in one\" src=\"http://discovercharlestonwv.com/files/20110824124815.jpg\" /></a></td>\r\n            <td width=\"160\" valign=\"top\" align=\"center\" style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 10px; PADDING-LEFT: 10px; PADDING-RIGHT: 10px; PADDING-TOP: 10px\"><a href=\"http://discovercharlestonwv.com/page.php?it=41\"><img width=\"150\" border=\"0\" height=\"188\" alt=\"Outdoor Recreation in Charleston WV\" src=\"http://discovercharlestonwv.com/files/20110824131416.jpg\" /></a>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td width=\"160\" valign=\"top\" align=\"center\" style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 10px; PADDING-LEFT: 10px; PADDING-RIGHT: 10px; PADDING-TOP: 10px\"><a href=\"http://discovercharlestonwv.com/page.php?it=37\"><img width=\"150\" border=\"0\" height=\"188\" alt=\"Waterways Waterpark, just south of Charleston for all your Family Fun!\" src=\"http://discovercharlestonwv.com/files/20110824142006.jpg\" /></a></td>\r\n            <td width=\"160\" valign=\"top\" align=\"center\" style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 10px; PADDING-LEFT: 10px; PADDING-RIGHT: 10px; PADDING-TOP: 10px\"><a href=\"http://discovercharlestonwv.com/page.php?it=43\"><img width=\"150\" border=\"0\" height=\"188\" alt=\"Mardi Gras Casino - True Casino Gaming in the Capitol City!\" src=\"http://discovercharlestonwv.com/files/20110824125949.jpg\" /></a></td>\r\n            <td width=\"160\" valign=\"top\" align=\"center\" style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 10px; PADDING-LEFT: 10px; PADDING-RIGHT: 10px; PADDING-TOP: 10px\"><a href=\"http://discovercharlestonwv.com/page.php?it=39\"><img width=\"150\" border=\"0\" height=\"188\" alt=\"Charleston WV, the entrance to the best whitewater rafting around, just 1 hour away!\" src=\"http://discovercharlestonwv.com/files/20110824141848.jpg\" /></a></td>\r\n            <td width=\"160\" valign=\"top\" align=\"center\" style=\"PADDING-BOTTOM: 10px; PADDING-LEFT: 10px; PADDING-RIGHT: 10px; PADDING-TOP: 10px\"><a href=\"http://discovercharlestonwv.com/page.php?it=40\"><img width=\"150\" border=\"0\" height=\"188\" alt=\"Shopping at Southridge, 100+ stores and restaurants to choose from!\" src=\"http://discovercharlestonwv.com/files/20110824144433.jpg\" /></a></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\">Please use our guide to learn more about our cities proud history, and to help you plan your next travel getaway to visit Charleston.&nbsp; <br /></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',	'Guide',	20080619100000,	'Charleston WV Travel Guide',	NULL,	NULL,	0,	20140228095247,	'left'),
(48,	'<div style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\" align=\"justify\"><font size=\"4\">We hope your visit here brings you all that you wish for. Take some time to explore and find a wonderful place full of hospitality, history, art, culture, music, fun and adventure! <br />We\'re located in the heart of the state as part of the largest Metro area and at the junction of 3 major interstates, I-64, I-77, &amp; I-79. Travel to and from the area is easy and beautiful no matter what season. <br />We invite you to sit back with us and take a view at some of the places nearby and hope you will enjoy your time here in our fair city.</font></div>',	'Photo',	20080619100000,	'Welcome to Charleston, West Virginia!',	NULL,	NULL,	0,	20110818091309,	'left'),
(49,	'<div style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><font size=\"4\">Our city can be the picturesque place for you to have your most important day. From our State Capitol grounds to the many parks, rivers and lakeside venues, for those with a eye to outdoor weddings, to our best hotel/conference venues for your indoor wedding (in case that stray rainstorm might come by).<br /><br />Please call us at (304)-414-4069 to discuss your ideas and what we can do to make your day the most special it can be! You can also visit us at the <a href=\"http://charlestonconferencecenter.com/weddings.php\">Charleston Conference Center Hotel Weddings Info Page</a>.</font></div>\r\n<br /><br /><br />',	'Wedding',	20080619100000,	'Charleston Weddings Gallery',	NULL,	NULL,	0,	20120125122500,	'left'),
(50,	'<h1 style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,102,0)\"><font size=\"4\">Charleston West Virginia Area Map</font></h1>\r\n<!-- Google map embed here --><iframe height=\"480\" marginheight=\"0\" src=\"http://maps.google.com/maps/ms?hl=en&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;msa=0&amp;msid=206036403575086106565.0004952cdb535b18530ca&amp;ll=38.341252,-81.679573&amp;spn=0.064627,0.109863&amp;z=13&amp;output=embed\" frameborder=\"0\" width=\"640\" marginwidth=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe><br /><small>View <a style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; COLOR: #0000ff\" href=\"http://maps.google.com/maps/ms?hl=en&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;msa=0&amp;msid=206036403575086106565.0004952cdb535b18530ca&amp;ll=38.341252,-81.679573&amp;spn=0.064627,0.109863&amp;z=13&amp;source=embed\">Hotel Locations</a> in a larger map</small> <!-- End of Google map embed --><hr color=\"#e8ede4\" size=\"1\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<h3 style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,102,0)\"><font size=\"3\">Directions to the&nbsp;Holiday Inn & Suites Charleston West<br />400 2nd Avenue, Charleston, WV </font></h3>\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><strong>Traveling from North</strong><br />I-77S/I-79S to I-64West toward Huntington, go 4 miles to Exit 56&mdash;Montrose Drive Exit, go right at light and get into the extreme right lane&mdash;bear to the right again, following Cloverleaf which will merge onto 2nd Avenue&mdash;go straight and the Holiday Inn & Suites Charleston West will be one block on your left. <br /><br /><strong>Traveling from South</strong><br />I-77N to I-64West, go 3 miles to Exit 56&mdash;Montrose Drive Exit, go right at light and get into the extreme right lane&mdash;bear to the right again, following Cloverleaf which will merge onto 2nd Avenue&mdash;go straight and the Charleston Conference Center will be one block on your left. <br /><br /><strong>Traveling from East</strong><br />I-64 West towards Huntington, take Exit 56&mdash;Montrose Drive Exit, go right at light and get into the extreme right lane&mdash;bear to the right again, following Cloverleaf which will merge onto 2nd Avenue&mdash;go straight and the Holiday Inn & Suites Charleston West will be one block on your left. <br /><br /><strong>Traveling from Yeager Airport </strong><br />Take exit to airport and follow road. It will turn into Greenbrier street at intersection, stay right at intersection and follow the signs for downtown Charleston. Take I-77N/I-64West until the two interstates split. Follow I-64, go 3 miles to Exit 56&mdash;Montrose Drive Exit, go right at light and get into the extreme right lane&mdash;bear to the right again, following Cloverleaf which will merge onto 2nd Avenue&mdash;go straight and the Holiday Inn & Suites Charleston West will be one block on your left. </p>\r\n<hr color=\"#e8ede4\" size=\"1\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<h3 style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,102,0)\"><font size=\"3\"><strong>Directions to Wingate by Wyndham Charleston <br />402 2nd Avenue,&nbsp;Charleston, WV</strong></font></h3>\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><strong>Traveling from North</strong><br />I-77S/I-79S to I-64West toward Huntington, go 4 miles to Exit 56&mdash;Montrose Drive Exit, go right at light and get into the extreme right lane&mdash;bear to the right again, following Cloverleaf which will merge onto 2nd Avenue&mdash;go straight and the Wingate will be one block on your left. <br /><br /><strong>Traveling from South</strong><br />h I-77N to I-64West, go 3 miles to Exit 56&mdash;Montrose Drive Exit, go right at light and get into the extreme right lane&mdash;bear to the right again, following Cloverleaf which will merge onto 2nd Avenue&mdash;go straight and the Wingate will be one block on your left.<br /><br /><strong>Traveling from East</strong><br />I-64 West towards Huntington, take Exit 56&mdash;Montrose Drive Exit, go right at light and get into the extreme right lane&mdash;bear to the right again, following Cloverleaf which will merge onto 2nd Avenue&mdash;go straight and the Wingate will be one block on your left.<br /><br /><strong>Traveling from West</strong><br />I-64 East towards Charleston, take Exit 56&mdash;Montrose Drive Exit, go right at light and get into the extreme right lane&mdash;bear to the right again, following Cloverleaf which will merge onto 2nd Avenue&mdash;go straight and the Wingate will be one block on your left. <br /><br /><strong>Traveling from Yeager Airport</strong><br />Take exit to airport and follow road. It will turn into Greenbrier street at intersection, stay right at intersection and follow the signs for downtown Charleston. Take I-77N/I-64West until the two interstates split. Follow I-64, go 3 miles to Exit 56&mdash;Montrose Drive Exit, go right at light and get into the extreme right lane&mdash;bear to the right again, following Cloverleaf which will merge onto 2nd Avenue&mdash;go straight and the Wingate will be one block on your left. </p>\r\n<hr color=\"#e8ede4\" size=\"1\" width=\"100%\" />\r\n<h3 style=\"COLOR: rgb(255,102,0)\"><font size=\"3\">Directions to the Hampton Inn Southridge <br />1 Preferred Place, Charleston, WV</font></h3>\r\n<p align=\"justify\"><strong>Traveling from North</strong><br />I-77S/I-79S to I-64West toward Huntington, go 3 miles to Exit 58A&mdash;Oakwood Road Exit, follow the exit ramp in the right lane to the end and turn right onto Route 119. Follow Rte. 119 for 4.5 miles. The Hampton Inn Southridge will be on the left.<br /><br /><strong>Traveling from South</strong><br />I-77N to I-64West toward Huntington, go 3 miles to Exit 58A&mdash;Oakwood Road Exit, follow the exit ramp in the right lane to the end and turn right onto Route 119. Follow Rte. 119 for 4.5 miles. The Hampton Inn Southridge will be on the left. <br /><br /><strong>Traveling from East</strong><br />I-64West toward Huntington, take Exit 58A&mdash;Oakwood Road Exit, follow the exit ramp in the right lane to the end and turn right onto Route 119. Follow Rte. 119 for 4.5 miles. The Hampton Inn Southridge will be on the left. <br /><br /><strong>Traveling from West</strong><br />I-64 East towards Charleston, take Exit 58A&mdash;Oakwood Road Exit, follow the exit ramp in the right lane to the end and turn right onto Route 119. Follow Rte. 119 for 4.5 miles. The Hampton Inn Southridge will be on the left. <br /><br /><strong>Traveling from Yeager Airport </strong><br />Take exit to airport and follow road. It will turn into Greenbrier street at intersection, stay right at intersection and follow the signs for downtown Charleston. Take I-77N/I-64West until the two interstates split. Follow I-64, go 3 miles to Exit 58A&mdash;Oakwood Road Exit, follow the exit ramp in the right lane to the end and turn right onto Route 119. Follow Rte. 119 for 4.5 miles. The Hampton Inn Southridge will be on the left.</p>',	'Maps',	20080619100000,	'Maps & Directions',	NULL,	NULL,	0,	20120525091107,	'left'),
(51,	'<h2 style=\"color: rgb(255, 102, 0);\"><font size=\"3\">Get relief from rising gas prices</font></h2>\r\n<p>Free Gas! Fill up the car and save when you stay with us. Get relief from  																				rising gas prices with the Gas Up and Getaway promotion. On your next stay at  																				the participating Ramada Charleston, Wingate by Wyndham, or Hampton Inn Southridge  																				you will receive:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>A $50 Gas card for a 5 night stay</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul> </ul>\r\n    <p>Not valid with negotiated rates or special discounts.  Redeemable only with an  																				email coupon from our website.  Based on availability. Must be for concurrent stays.</p>\r\n    <p>To benefit from the Gas Up and Getaway promotion, simply complete the form below  																				and we will send you a gas coupon. Tell us some basic information about your visit  																				and present the coupon upon check in at the front desk. </p>\r\n    <hr />\r\n    <table align=\"center\">\r\n        <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n                <td><font size=\"2\">First Name: </font></td>\r\n                <td><input type=\"text\" name=\"First_Name\" /></td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n                <td><font size=\"2\">Last Name: </font></td>\r\n                <td><input type=\"text\" name=\"Last_Name\" /></td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n                <td><font size=\"2\">Approximate Date of Visit: </font></td>\r\n                <td><input type=\"text\" name=\"Approx_Dates\" /></td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n                <td><font size=\"2\">Email Address: </font></td>\r\n                <td><input type=\"text\" name=\"Email_Address\" /></td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n                <td><font size=\"2\">A $20 Gas card for a 2 night stay: </font></td>\r\n                <td><input type=\"radio\" value=\"20 Dollars for a 2 Night Stay\" name=\"Coupon_Type