uot;; FONT-SIZE: 13pt\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" align=\"right\" width=\"250\" height=\"318\" src=\"http://discovercharlestonwv.com/files/20110818074258.jpg\" />In part an outdoor farmers&rsquo; market and in part a gourmet shopping center, Charleston, West Virginia&rsquo;s Capital Market just off I-77 features everything from fresh produce and flowers, to a beautiful selection of wine and cheese, fresh produce stalls, Ellen&rsquo;s Homemade Ice Cream, Holl&rsquo;s chocolate, Capitol Roasters, to Fresh Seafood Company. With a wonderful restaurant on site, Charleston&rsquo;s own Soho&rsquo;s Italian Restaurant, The Capitol Market can make for a truly beautiful day! </span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"justify\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Arial&quot;, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 13pt\">Originally a transfer dock and warehouse for the New York Central Railroad Company, this neglected storehouse was revitalized in the mid-1990s, and transformed as part of the city&rsquo;s &ldquo;Charleston Renaissance<span style=\"COLOR: #1f497d\">&rdquo;</span>.</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"justify\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Arial&quot;, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 13pt\">Each season brings a different look to this marketplace, but one things for sure upon entering you will find a beautiful atmosphere full of fresh flowers and open air where devoted members of the community bring the farm to this urban setting.</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"justify\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Arial&quot;, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 13pt\">Head inside to the Capital Market, and discover what all that lies between these red-brick walls and beautiful archways.&nbsp; The beautiful modern art and handmade crafts in between all of the vendors makes for quite the experience!&nbsp; From gourmet food to natural and historical relics, the Capital Market is a great place to stop in or spend the day!</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: &quot;Arial&quot;, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 13pt\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" align=\"middle\" width=\"600\" height=\"354\" src=\"http://discovercharlestonwv.com/files/20110818075022.jpg\" /></span></strong></p>',	0,	0,	NULL,	NULL,	NULL,	0),
