(96,	2,	'2015-06-22 12:42:52',	'2015-06-22 16:42:52',	'<strong>A Clockwork Orange</strong>\r\n\r\nIn future Britain, delinquent, ultraviolent youth Alex DeLarge is jailed for horrible crimes against humanity. In an effort to commute his sentence, Alex volunteers for an experimental aversion therapy developed by the government in an effort to solve society\'s crime problem - but not all goes according to plan. Alex\'s ordeals are far from over once he hits the mean streets of Britain that he had a hand in creating. Considered by many to be one of director Stanley Kubricks masterworks, this multi-Oscar nominated film stars Malcolm McDowell and Patrick Magee. \r\n\r\nJoin us for new classic science fiction films. Films are only $6 per person.',	'Digital Dome: Science Fiction Film Night',	'',	'publish',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'digital-dome-science-fiction-film-night',	'',	'',	'2015-06-22 12:42:52',	'2015-06-22 16:42:52',	'',	0,	'http://localhost:8888/discovercharleston/?post_type=chronosly&#038;p=96',	0,	'chronosly',	'',	0),
