es a free, family friendly movie\r\n\r\ntheater under the stars. The Island opens up at 6 with a Kids Zone &amp; the movie will start around\r\n\r\ndusk! Movie Nights take place Wednesday nights in June.\r\n\r\n  \r\n\r\nBest Time of the Year\r\n\r\nAll year long there\'s plenty of Family Fun in Charleston, WV!',	'Family Fun',	'',	'inherit',	'open',	'open',	'',	'202-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2015-06-29 11:15:28',	'2015-06-29 15:15:28',	'',	202,	'http://localhost:8888/discovercharleston/uncategorized/202-revision-v1',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
