 Tour.\r\n<h3>Bridge Day</h3>\r\nBridge Day, one of the largest extreme sports event in the world, is held annually on the third Saturday in October in Fayette County, West Virginia (WV). Hundreds of BASE jumpers and nearly 80,000 spectators are expected to attend the event. Vendor booths and food are available on the bridge, along with the best overlook of the New River Gorge.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Best Time of the Year</h3>\r\nFall is a great time to catch some great (and unique) events for adrenaline junkies.  September and October offer good weather but not hot conditions.\r\n\r\n</div>',	'Adrenaline Junkie',	'',	'inherit',	'open',	'open',	'',	'206-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2015-06-30 13:04:14',	'2015-06-30 17:04:14',	'',	206,	'http://localhost:8888/discovercharleston/uncategorized/206-revision-v1',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
