ams consist of baseball, basketball, football, golf, tennis, softball, cross country and volleyball.\r\n<p class=\"content-block cbaddress\">500 Fairlawn Ave.\r\nInstitute, WV 25112\r\n<a href=\"http://www.wvsuyellowjackets.com\" target=\"_blank\">wvsuyellowjackets.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"content-block col-2-cb\">\r\n<h3>Charleston Civic Center</h3>\r\nHosts a variety of annual sporting events including WVSSAC Boys and Girls Basketball State Tournaments, archery and volleyball tournaments, Mountain East Conference Championships, boxing/martial arts events, Capital Classic between WVU and Marshall Men\'s Basketball.\r\n<p class=\"content-block cbaddress\">200 Civic Center Dr.\r\nCharleston, WV 25301\r\n<a href=\"http://www.charlestonwvciviccenter.com\" target=\"_blank\">www.charlestonwvciviccenter.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Trace Fork Soccer Complex</h3>\r\nThe Friends of Coal Fields At Trace Fork Soccer Complex is a six field soccer complex is located at the Shops at Trace Fork, just off U.S. Rt. 119 south of Charleston, West Virginia.\r\n<p class=\"content-block cbaddress\">25 RHL Blvd.\r\nSouth Charleston, WV 25309\r\n<a href=\"http://traceforksoccer.com/\" target=\"_blank\">traceforksoccer.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Adelphia Sports Bar and Grille</h3>\r\nVoted best appetizer and wings in the valley three years in a row! Adelphia infuses Greek and American cuisine to offer some of the best food around. Open 365 days a year and full menu served until midnight and later.\r\n<p class=\"content-block cbaddress\">218 Capitol Street\r\nCharleston WV, 25301\r\n<a href=\"http://adelphiasportsbar.com/\" target=\"_blank\">http://adelphiasportsbar.com/</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>South Charleston Memorial Ice Arena</h3>\r\nNewly opened, state-of-the-art facility with amenities like an arcade and heated seating area that will accommodate 500 spectators. Groups of all sizes are welcome.\r\n<p class=\"content-block cbaddress\">20 RHL Blvd.\r\nCharleston, WV 25309\r\n<a href=\"