(904,	2,	'2015-07-16 14:27:45',	'2015-07-16 18:27:45',	'Founded in 1992, Willow Creek Association (WCA) is the organization behind The Global Leadership Summit. We serve pioneering pastors and leaders around the world by curating inspirational leadership, intentional skill development and experiences that help local churches thrive.\r\n\r\nThe Global Leadership Summit is a two-day event that is telecast LIVE from Willow\'s campus near Chicago every August to more than 300 locations and 90,000 people in North America. Then, throughout the fall, International Summit events take place in an additional 350+ cities, in 105 countries - translated into over 50 languages, with over 150,000 leaders attending.\r\n\r\nLasy year over 150 leaders representing over 30 organizations came to the Summit for the first time ever in Charleston, WV!\r\n\r\nSouthridge Church is thrilled to be bringing the Global Leadership Summit to the Charleston area again this year as a Premier Host Site. We hope to see YOU at the Summit!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;',	'Global Leadership Summit - Broadcast',	'',	'publish',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'global-leadership-summit-broadcast',	'',	'',	'2015-08-06 09:47:21',	'2015-08-06 13:47:21',	'',	0,	'http://localhost:8888/discovercharleston/?post_type=chronosly&#038;p=904',	0,	'chronosly',	'',	0),
