(1467,	3,	'2015-08-19 16:15:53',	'2015-08-19 20:15:53',	'Mountain Mission Incorporated is hosting the Pack the Pantry 5K Run/Walk on Saturday, August 29 beginning and ending at the Charleston Area Alliance. Registration is at 8:30 a.m., and the race begins at 9:00 a.m. All proceeds go toward packing the Mountain Mission pantry to help families across Kanawha County all year long.\r\n\r\nAug. 3-14 - Early Bird Registration: $25\r\n** Guaranteed a t-shirt\r\nAug. 15-28 - Registration: $30\r\nAug. 29 - Day of Race Registration: $35\r\n\r\nAwards will be given to the top overall male and female finisher and the top 3 finishers in each age group for the 5K run. The overall winners will not be eligible for awards in their age groups.\r\n\r\nDonations are also welcomed and appreciated.',	'Pack the Pantry 5k Run/Walk',	'',	'publish',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'pack-the-pantry-5k-runwalk',	'',	'',	'2015-08-19 16:15:53',	'2015-08-19 20:15:53',	'',	0,	'http://localhost:8888/discovercharleston/?post_type=chronosly&#038;p=1467',	0,	'chronosly',	'',	0),
